Name: Nyanco Space
About the game: It was a beautiful Sunday afternoon and Nyanco was happily taking a stroll. All was well. Until aliens suddenly appeared and abducted Nyanco! You and her were scheduled to waltz together, but she's been taken away! Can you save Nyanco? Your adventure to save her begins! Various Adventures 6 Worlds, 48 Stages, Boss Battles, SF Fantasy, Christmas, Halloween, Space, and More! Features Old School Arcade Game Experience Simple Yet Addictive Casual Gameplay Recommended For Nyanco Channel Fans Special rewards include illustrations of Nyanco Game Engine RPG Maker VX Ace Disclaimer Nyanco Space is fictional. Any resemblance to the real world is purely coincidental. Special Thanks Alice, nashix, Holy Lightning, HaZE, ParanoX, and You!
